  "instructions": {
    "1": "Bring the water to a boil in a medium saucepan over high heat. Add the salt and slowly stir in the grits. Reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, stirring occasionally, for 20 minutes, or until the grits are creamy and thickened. Remove from the heat.",
